{"id": 948, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的哪种消费行为通常不被理解？", "description": "在小众消费的世界里，我是孤独寂寞的花朵。（题图来自：Victor Beuren）", "record_count": 3676, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183841pGfUgyjVweEW2mDX.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-03T11:09:41Z", "options": [{"id": 73728, "content": "购买各种独立出版的图书总被不理解", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 592963}, {"id": 73729, "content": "买李宇春演唱会门票！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572478}, {"id": 73730, "content": "一分钱不花", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363108}, {"id": 73986, "content": "囤货 比如卫生纸面巾纸卫生巾化妆水乳液护手霜身体乳粉底睫毛膏口红等等 满满三大抽屉???", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586732}, {"id": 80642, "content": "去吃什么意大利，德国什么的进口冰淇淋球，25一个球的，50一个的，100一个的...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617678}, {"id": 73731, "content": "上拳击私教课，一对一的那种。我就是喜欢怎样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518134}, {"id": 73732, "content": "买几百块的耳机是因为买不起几千块的SAD", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469507}, {"id": 73733, "content": "买的再难看的书也要忍着看完...", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593451}, {"id": 73989, "content": "疯狂的迷恋电子产品！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595155}, {"id": 74245, "content": "买衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593896}, {"id": 73734, "content": "花钱买正版App……", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 453039}, {"id": 73735, "content": "买kindle", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126131}, {"id": 73736, "content": "收集G-shock", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546955}, {"id": 73737, "content": "剑三点卡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591933}, {"id": 73738, "content": "买了打蛋器，结果打蛋还是用筷子", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594450}, {"id": 73739, "content": "买了打蛋器，结果打蛋的时候还是用筷子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594450}, {"id": 73740, "content": "为了拍照好看买一堆刀叉盘和", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594466}, {"id": 73741, "content": "为了降价买买买，而不是自己需要才买！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566363}, {"id": 73742, "content": "老师在上课问有没有买过正版软件我说有的时候同学一脸惊愕", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319909}, {"id": 79630, "content": "什么？有盗版游戏不玩买好几百块的正版玩？你这不是傻X么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579354}, {"id": 73999, "content": "两千买个键帽，对，是一个键帽", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573899}, {"id": 73744, "content": "按照自己能承受的范围 买能买得起的最贵的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 594505}, {"id": 74000, "content": "都快毕业了还花钱培训。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416801}, {"id": 73745, "content": "一些东西（比如书，文具）会买两件，一件自用，一件以防需要借人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 153490}, {"id": 74001, "content": "网上随便就可以找到盗版，却去电影院看电影，或者买纸质书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416801}, {"id": 73748, "content": "四位数的电动牙刷和洁面仪...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552207}, {"id": 73749, "content": "一个星期买9个腮红", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593216}, {"id": 73750, "content": "steam +1", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 489270}, {"id": 77846, "content": "买收纳整理的东西。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607124}, {"id": 73751, "content": "其你们想说的是\n只要是花钱了\n不管有没有必要\n都是不能理解的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 38139}, {"id": 76568, "content": "買手辦啊買手辦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602693}, {"id": 73753, "content": "应该还有一个”你对别人的哪些消费行为不理解”的调查吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179877}, {"id": 73754, "content": "鞋一定要买正品，而且有n多双同种类型的运动鞋 板鞋…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508674}, {"id": 75546, "content": "上学的时候，心水的文具每样两份，一份用，一份藏；进书店，一定要买书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78574}, {"id": 73755, "content": "买各种昂贵的乐器...被说自己不专心精通一个QAQ其实我是想找到适合我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530218}, {"id": 73756, "content": "一个人看电影、话剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 392224}, {"id": 79900, "content": "飞去看我心爱歌手的演唱会。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614757}, {"id": 73757, "content": "作为一个姑娘，花很少的钱买衣服，却花很多钱买游戏和科技产品…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495261}, {"id": 73758, "content": "耳机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294948}, {"id": 77342, "content": "衣服常买深色系，黑色我最爱啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 359853}, {"id": 73759, "content": "白衬衫，纯白衬衫，不同的款式，总被认为是不换衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529184}, {"id": 85023, "content": "买各种玻璃杯，玻璃瓶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 634810}, {"id": 73760, "content": "收费的单机手游 音游", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 532724}, {"id": 73761, "content": "昂贵的品牌手机壳", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512590}, {"id": 73762, "content": "买宅物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "sel